Program: Discovery
Title: Influenza - waiting for a pandemic
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryw6
Last Broadcast Date: 07 December 2004
Experts discuss and agree on how an influenza pandemic is imminent. Is a flu pandemic on the scale of the 1918 outbreak likely? Scientists believe there a real threat and that when a flu pandemic strikes it will be on the level of a major global catastrophe. Presenter: Peter Evans. Producer: Alexandra Feachem. Show less